<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Challenge Not Approved – OnlyFunds</title>
  <style>
    body { 
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif; 
      margin:0; 
      padding:20px; 
      background:#f5f5f5; 
      color:#333; 
    }
    .email-container { 
      max-width:400px; 
      margin:0 auto; 
      background:#fff; 
      padding:20px; 
      border-radius:8px; 
      box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
    }
    .banner { 
      width:100%; 
      height:auto; 
      border-radius:8px 8px 0 0; 
      margin-bottom:20px; 
    }
    .title { 
      color:#333; 
      font-size:24px; 
      font-weight:bold; 
      margin-bottom:30px; 
    }
    .user-greeting { 
      color:#333; 
      font-size:18px; 
      font-weight:bold; 
      margin-bottom:20px; 
    }
    .main-message { 
      color:#333; 
      font-size:16px; 
      font-weight:bold; 
      margin-bottom:20px; 
    }
    .description { 
      color:#666; 
      font-size:14px; 
      line-height:1.4; 
      margin-bottom:15px; 
    }
    .challenge-box { 
      background:#fff; 
      padding:15px; 
      border-radius:6px; 
      border:2px solid #007bff; 
      margin:20px 0; 
    }
    .highlight { 
      color:#007bff; 
      font-weight:bold; 
    }
    .status-info { 
      color:#333; 
      font-size:14px; 
      margin-bottom:8px; 
    }
    .amount-highlight { 
      color:#6c757d; 
      font-weight:bold; 
      font-size:18px; 
    }
    .violation-box { 
      background:#fef2f2; 
      padding:15px; 
      border-radius:6px; 
      border:2px solid #dc2626; 
      margin:20px 0; 
    }
    .violation-text { 
      color:#dc2626; 
      font-weight:bold; 
      font-size:14px; 
      line-height:1.4; 
    }
    .reason-box { 
      background:#fff3cd; 
      padding:15px; 
      border-radius:6px; 
      border:2px solid #ffc107; 
      margin:20px 0; 
    }
    .reason-text { 
      color:#856404; 
      font-weight:bold; 
      font-size:14px; 
      line-height:1.6; 
    }
    .action-button { 
      background:#007bff; 
      color:#ffffff; 
      padding:12px 20px; 
      border:none; 
      border-radius:6px; 
      font-size:16px; 
      font-weight:bold; 
      width:100%; 
      margin:10px 0; 
      text-align:center; 
      text-decoration:none; 
      display:block; 
      cursor:pointer; 
      box-sizing:border-box; 
    }
    .action-button:hover { 
      background:#0056b3; 
      color:#ffffff; 
    }
    .action-button-secondary { 
      background:#6c757d; 
      color:#ffffff; 
      padding:12px 20px; 
      border:none; 
      border-radius:6px; 
      font-size:14px; 
      font-weight:bold; 
      width:100%; 
      margin:10px 0; 
      text-align:center; 
      text-decoration:none; 
      display:block; 
      cursor:pointer; 
      box-sizing:border-box; 
    }
    .footer-text { 
      color:#666; 
      font-size:12px; 
      margin-top:20px; 
    }
    .copyright { 
      color:#999; 
      font-size:11px; 
      margin-top:15px; 
      text-align:center; 
    }
    .company-name { 
      color:#007bff; 
      font-weight:bold; 
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="email-container">
    {{#if banner}}
    <img src="{{banner}}" alt="OnlyFunds Banner" class="banner">
    {{/if}}
    
    <div class="title">Challenge Not Approved</div>
    
    <div class="user-greeting">Hello Trader</div>
    
    <div class="main-message">Your challenge was not approved</div>
    
    <div class="description">
      We've reviewed your trading challenge and found that some rules were violated. Please review the details below and don't worry, you can try again!
    </div>
    
    <div class="challenge-box">
      <div class="status-info"><strong>Challenge Type:</strong> <span class="highlight">{{challenge_type}}</span></div>
      <div class="status-info"><strong>Account Size:</strong> <span class="amount-highlight">${{account_size}}</span></div>
      <div class="status-info"><strong>Challenge ID:</strong> <span class="highlight">{{challenge_id}}</span></div>
      <div class="status-info"><strong>Status:</strong> <span style="color:#dc2626; font-weight:bold;">Not Approved</span></div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="reason-box">
      <div class="status-info"><strong>Reason for Disapproval:</strong></div>
      <div class="reason-text">{{disapproval_reason}}</div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="description">
      You can review your performance metrics and the detailed breakdown in your dashboard. Our support team is available to help you understand these requirements better.
    </div>
    
    <a href="{{landingUrl}}" class="action-button" target="_blank">View Performance</a>
    
    <a href="{{new_challenge_url}}" class="action-button-secondary" target="_blank">Start New Challenge</a>
    
    <div class="description">
      <span class="highlight">Our team is here to help you succeed!</span>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer-text">
      Best regards,<br><br>
      <span class="company-name">OnlyFunds</span> Team
    </div>
    
    <div class="copyright">
      © 2025 <span class="company-name">OnlyFunds</span>. All rights reserved.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>